{"tid":2272794,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"女星 Lashana Lynch 將於《#007：#生死有時》中繼任007","createTime":"2020-11-05T09:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T02:44:58.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d4404ba55c4c76aa8737b68d8a456474bda30f19","tid":2272794,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"女星 Lashana Lynch 將於《#007：#生死有時》中繼任007<br />\n<br />\n消息由舊年就開始傳出 Lashana Lynch 繼任007，但一直冇人證實。近日佢終於喺 Harper&rsquo;s Bazaar 雜誌訪談中正式親口承認，佢將會喺戲中繼承 James Bond 退休後嘅 007 頭銜，成為首位黑人女 007。《007：生死有時》延期左幾次，最新映期為出年4月1日。<br />\n<br />\n《007：生死有時》電影資料 <a href=\"https://enjoymovie.net/movies/9vwJYqQw5X/no-time-to-die\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fenjoymovie.net%2Fmovies%2F9vwJYqQw5X%2Fno-time-to-die&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4GaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=7ecc0458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://enjoymovie.net/movies/9vwJYqQw5X/no-time-to-die</a><br />\n<br />\n《007：生死有時》故事簡介<br />\n由英國影帝級紅星丹尼爾基克，好評五度飾演007占士邦，聯同上一集性感法國女星蕾雅絲端，暨《波希米亞狂想曲》出爐奧斯卡影帝雷米馬利克及《神探白朗：福比利大宅謀殺案》古巴索女安娜德哈瑪斯強勢加盟，成為2020首部舉世注目的荷里活超級鉅製。 占士邦原本在牙買加享受低調人生，但安穩一時，迎上無限美女、未知危機和槍林彈雨，才是真正的特務風骨！他的一位 CIA 舊友 Felix Leiter 突然現身求助，表面上的任務只是營救被綁架科學家，查探下去卻發現背後陰謀超乎想像，令他身陷神秘黑手主宰的高科技殺局...<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 <a href=\"https://screenrant.com/no-time-die-new-007-lashana-lynch-bond/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Fno-time-die-new-007-lashana-lynch-bond%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4GaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=20b71e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://screenrant.com/no-time-die-new-007-lashana-lynch-bond/</a><br />\n<br />\n=======<br />\n✴️ 各大平台有乜好睇? Netflix、iTunes 同戲院資訊，盡在 Enjoy Movie App<br />\niOS 立即下載 &gt;&gt; <a href=\"https://go.enjoymovie.net/17a81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.enjoymovie.net%2F17a81&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4GaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=d33acfa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://go.enjoymovie.net/17a81</a><br />\n<br />\n